

<div class="modal-dialog">
    <div class="modal-content">
        <div id='myModalContent'>
            <div class="container ">
                <h2 class="text-center">Subscribe now</h2>
                <p>
                    What will you get for subscribing? 
                    <br />
                    <br />
                    We are not here to fill your inbox with spam and the only information you will receive from us includes:
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            New Gold and Silver ICO listings.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            A weekly email that includes:
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Link to the top YouTube video of the week.</li>
                                <li>Spreadsheet with the top rated ICO’s</li>
